messages.messageBody: Liked “Perfect, I will update the coverages right away for my senior agent Noah Wamboldt. You should be getting an update from him soon as he works on getting this finished up for you.”
I received it! And I forwarded my declaration page to you.
Liked “Monday at 11 am sounds great. I will schedule that in now and I look forward to speaking with you Monday morning. I hope you have a great weekend.”
